---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Dr Delhasse — Cardiologist in Sion and Valais" description="Cardiology and internal medicine consultations at the CIC Clinic in Saxon, Valais. Personalised care, cardiac examinations, comprehensive follow-up." lang="en">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero__video-wrap">
      <video class="hero__video" autoplay muted loop playsinline preload="auto" poster="/images/ecg-poster.jpg">
        <source src="/videos/ecg-hero.webm" type="video/webm" />
        <source src="/videos/ecg-hero.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
      </video>
      <div class="hero__overlay"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero__content container">
      <div class="hero__ecg-line"></div>
      <h1 class="hero__title">One sees clearly only<br />with the <span class="text-primary">heart</span></h1>
      <p class="hero__quote">"What is essential is invisible to the eye."<br /><em>— Antoine de Saint-Exupéry</em></p>
      <div class="hero__actions">
        <a href="/en/contact" class="btn btn--primary">Book an appointment</a>
        <a href="/en/about" class="btn btn--outline">About Dr. Delhasse</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Consultation Process -->
  <section class="section process">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center" style="margin-bottom: 3rem;">
        <h2>How does an appointment with your <span class="text-primary">cardiologist</span> work?</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="process__grid grid grid--4">
        <div class="process__card">
          <div class="process__number">01</div>
          <img src="/images/le-bilan.webp" alt="The check-up" class="process__img" loading="lazy" width="400" height="180" />
          <h3>The Check-up</h3>
          <p>A cardiology check-up provides an in-depth assessment of heart health to detect risks or diseases.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="process__card">
          <div class="process__number">02</div>
          <img src="/images/prise-informations.webp" alt="Information gathering" class="process__img" loading="lazy" width="400" height="180" />
          <h3>Information Gathering</h3>
          <p>After reviewing medical and family history as well as lifestyle, the physician performs a clinical exam, including blood-pressure measurement and cardiac auscultation.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="process__card">
          <div class="process__number">03</div>
          <img src="/images/examen.webp" alt="The exam" class="process__img" loading="lazy" width="400" height="180" />
          <h3>The Exam</h3>
          <p>Depending on findings, tests such as electrocardiograms, echocardiography or exercise testing may be prescribed. Blood tests often complete the work-up to assess risk factors like cholesterol or diabetes.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="process__card">
          <div class="process__number">04</div>
          <img src="/images/resultats.webp" alt="The results" class="process__img" loading="lazy" width="400" height="180" />
          <h3>The Results</h3>
          <p>After the evaluation, the doctor explains the results, proposes a personalised plan with advice and treatment options, and arranges follow-up if necessary to prevent or effectively treat cardiovascular disease.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About CTA -->
  <section class="section section--navy about-cta">
    <div class="container about-cta__inner">
      <div class="about-cta__text">
        <h2>A heart healing hearts</h2>
        <p>Read my story and my commitment.</p>
        <a href="/en/about" class="btn btn--outline">Learn more</a>
      </div>
      <div class="about-cta__image">
        <img src="/images/dr-delhasse.jpeg" alt="Dr. Sébastien Delhasse" width="500" height="600" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Heart & You -->
  <section class="section section--gray services">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center" style="margin-bottom: 3rem;">
        <h2>Your Heart <span class="text-primary">&</span> You</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid--3">
        <a href="/en/symptoms" class="service-card">
          <img src="/images/question-medicale.webp" alt="Symptoms" class="service-card__img" loading="lazy" width="400" height="220" />
          <div class="service-card__body">
            <h3>Symptoms to Watch</h3>
            <span class="service-card__link">Learn more →</span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/en/areas-of-expertise" class="service-card">
          <img src="/images/collaboration.webp" alt="Areas of Expertise" class="service-card__img" loading="lazy" width="400" height="220" />
          <div class="service-card__body">
            <h3>Areas of Expertise</h3>
            <span class="service-card__link">Learn more →</span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/en/cardiac-examinations" class="service-card">
          <img src="/images/demande-rdv.webp" alt="Cardiological Examinations" class="service-card__img" loading="lazy" width="400" height="220" />
          <div class="service-card__body">
            <h3>Cardiological Examinations</h3>
            <span class="service-card__link">Learn more →</span>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Trust Bar -->
  <section class="section trust-bar">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="trust-bar__grid">
        <div class="trust-bar__item">
          <div class="trust-bar__number">FMH</div>
          <p>Member of the Swiss Medical Association</p>
        </div>
        <div class="trust-bar__item">
          <div class="trust-bar__number">ESC</div>
          <p>European Society of Cardiology</p>
        </div>
        <div class="trust-bar__item">
          <div class="trust-bar__number">3</div>
          <p>Consultation languages: FR, EN, DE</p>
        </div>
        <div class="trust-bar__item">
          <div class="trust-bar__number">CIC</div>
          <p>CIC Clinic Saxon — State-of-the-art equipment</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact CTA -->
  <section class="section section--navy cta">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center" style="margin-bottom: 3rem;">
        <h2>Book an appointment</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="cta__cards grid grid--3">
        <div class="cta-card">
          <h3>Appointment Request</h3>
          <p>Need a cardiology consultation in Sion or anywhere else in Valais? Request an appointment — it's quick and secure.</p>
          <a href="/en/contact" class="btn btn--primary">Contact us</a>
        </div>
        <div class="cta-card">
          <h3>Simple Medical Question</h3>
          <p>Ask a brief question. Get a prompt, professional answer.</p>
          <a href="/en/contact" class="btn btn--primary">Contact us</a>
        </div>
        <div class="cta-card">
          <h3>Collaboration or Other</h3>
          <p>For any collaboration proposal, conference, or other specific request.</p>
          <a href="/en/contact" class="btn btn--primary">Contact us</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    color: var(--color-white);
    padding: 10rem 0 7rem;
    min-height: 80vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero__video-wrap { position: absolute; inset: 0; z-index: 0; }
  .hero__video { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; object-position: center 60%; }
  .hero__overlay {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background:
      linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(21, 50, 89, 0.88) 0%, rgba(26, 61, 109, 0.75) 50%, rgba(21, 50, 89, 0.92) 100%),
      linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0%, transparent 30%, transparent 70%, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3) 100%);
  }
  .hero__content { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
  .hero__ecg-line { width: 60px; height: 3px; background: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: 2rem; border-radius: 2px; opacity: 0.8; }
  .hero__title { font-size: 3.75rem; color: var(--color-white); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.1; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
  .hero__quote { font-size: 1.15rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65); margin-bottom: 2.5rem; max-width: 480px; line-height: 1.6; }
  .hero__quote em { font-size: 0.9rem; opacity: 0.6; }
  .hero__actions { display: flex; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }

  .process__card { background: var(--color-white); border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.06); transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease; }
  .process__card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
  .process__number { padding: 1.25rem 1.25rem 0; font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-primary); opacity: 0.3; }
  .process__img { width: 100%; height: 180px; object-fit: cover; }
  .process__card h3 { padding: 1rem 1.25rem 0.5rem; font-size: 1.1rem; }
  .process__card p { padding: 0 1.25rem 1.5rem; font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.5; }

  .about-cta__inner { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 4rem; align-items: center; }
  .about-cta__text h2 { color: var(--color-white); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .about-cta__text p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .about-cta__image img { border-radius: 8px; width: 100%; max-width: 400px; }

  .service-card { display: block; background: var(--color-white); border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.06); transition: all 0.3s ease; text-decoration: none; }
  .service-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
  .service-card__img { width: 100%; height: 200px; object-fit: cover; }
  .service-card__body { padding: 1.5rem; }
  .service-card h3 { margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .service-card__link { color: var(--color-primary); font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.9rem; }

  .cta-card { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius: 8px; padding: 2rem; text-align: center; transition: all 0.3s ease; }
  .cta-card:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); }
  .cta-card h3 { color: var(--color-white); margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 1.15rem; }
  .cta-card p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); font-size: 0.95rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }

  .trust-bar { padding: 4rem 0; background: var(--color-white); border-top: 1px solid #eee; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; }
  .trust-bar__grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 2rem; text-align: center; }
  .trust-bar__item { padding: 1.5rem 1rem; }
  .trust-bar__number { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; letter-spacing: 0.02em; }
  .trust-bar__item p { font-size: 0.85rem; line-height: 1.4; color: var(--color-gray); margin: 0; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero { padding: 7rem 0 4rem; min-height: 60vh; }
    .trust-bar__grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 1rem; }
    .hero__video { object-position: 65% center; }
    .hero__ecg-line { width: 40px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    .hero__title { font-size: 2.25rem; }
    .about-cta__inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem; text-align: center; }
    .about-cta__image img { margin: 0 auto; }
  }
</style>
